title: Karz Chukana Hai
subTitle: After losing his job owing to his arrogance and subsequently his son, Vijay, Atmaram realises his mistake and decides to turn over a new leaf.

title: Jaisi Karni Waisi Bharni
subTitle: A conniving son throws his aged parents out of the house. Years later, he meets the same fate when his son decides to teach him a lesson.

title: Aan Baan
subTitle: Raja Bahadur indulges in various unlawful activities and is always saved by his brother, Suraj. When he decides to marry Rekha, Suraj, who is also in love with her, falls into a dilemma.

title: Angel
subTitle: Abhay returns from prison after running over a man and falls for the victim's daughter daughter. However, when her brother sees them in a compromising position, he accuses Abhay of assaulting her.

title: Shiva
subTitle: Shiva, a fresher at VAC College, is forced to stand up against the students' union president and a group of gangsters who have made the college environment increasingly violent.

title: Rickshawala
subTitle: Gopi, a humble rickshaw puller, faces love and social prejudice as he pursues a relationship with Kiran, a woman from a higher class, challenging societal norms and personal conflicts.

title: Prem Kahani
subTitle: Rajesh, an apolitical poet, is in love with Kamini and leads a peaceful life. However, when his brother is killed by the British government, he decides to become a revolutionary and joins the freedom struggle.

title: Dil Kya Kare
subTitle: The parents of an adopted child face issues of love, betrayal and custody when their daughter's birth mother arrives.

title: Raj Kumar
subTitle: Rajkumar's mother sets out to oppose his marriage after she finds out that he plans to marry the rival kingdom's princess.

title: Raj Kumar
subTitle: Rajkumar's mother sets out to oppose his marriage after she finds out that he plans to marry the rival kingdom's princess.

title: Ram Avtar
subTitle: Childhood friends Ram and Avtar face a love triangle when Ram falls for Sangeeta, whom Avtar also loves. Ram sacrifices his love for Avtar, but their enemy Gundappaswami threatens to expose the truth.

title: Swarag Se Sunder
subTitle: Two brothers struggle to keep their family together as external forces like the younger brother's father-in-law try to break them apart.

title: Hotel Milan
subTitle: Vipul and Saurabh, two friends, decide to put an end to the misery of couples by starting a love hotel. However, the local political group is not in favour of their venture.

title: Mera Muqadaar
subTitle: Shanti and Suraj lead a content life until he abandons her to marry Ruchi. Shanti and Ruchi both give birth to boys, who grow up and fight each other, unaware that they are half-brothers.

title: Inteqam
subTitle: When Birju's sister, Chhaya, is raped and the court fails to mete out justice, his parents die due to the shock. Birju sets out to seek revenge and kidnaps Dinanath's sister.

title: Deewana Tere Naam Ka
subTitle: Friends Shankar and Shambhu share a lot in common and also end up falling in love with the same girl. However, when the girl loves Shankar, Shambhu parts ways with him and joins his rival.

title: Disco Dancer
subTitle: A slum-dwelling performer finds a new calling as a rising disco star. However, things take an unfortunate turn when an enemy from the past reappears in his life.

title: Jaanwar
subTitle: A criminal changes the course of his life when he decides to raise a baby who has survived a train crash, but chaos ensues when his past begins to haunt him.

title: Rajaji
subTitle: Raja, a young man, wants an easy life and marries for wealth and comfort. He soon finds out that there is an underlying secret of his wife and feels trapped.

title: 3 Deewarein
subTitle: While filming a documentary in a prison, Chandrika comes across three unique stories and, somewhere in between, finds what her heart has been seeking.

title: 3 Deewarein
subTitle: While filming a documentary in a prison, Chandrika comes across three unique stories and, somewhere in between, finds what her heart has been seeking.

title: Jail Yatra
subTitle: After landing multiple times in prison due to his hopeless nature, Raju gets caught up with an infamous gangster and tries to escape him.

title: Ab Kya Hoga
subTitle: A young man stumbles upon a mysterious woman, who he suspects of being a ghost. However, his worst fears come true when his mother arranges his marriage with the same woman.

title: Laila
subTitle: Deshraj and Leela's love thrives under the shadows of enmity between two Rajput families. This triggers a clash of expectations, egos, and bullets, placing several lives in danger.

title: Bazaar
subTitle: Najma is in love with Akhtar but cannot marry him until he is financially stable. An elderly Shakir promises to help Akhtar set up his business in exchange for Najma finding a suitable bride for him.

title: Amba
subTitle: When Amba gets her son Rajendra arrested for sexually assaulting their servant's daughter, Rajendra's wife wreaks havoc into their lives as she vows to avenge him.

title: Gharana
subTitle: Prem Mehra loses everything after one of his employees joins hands with his rapacious rival and the two plot against him. Later, his sons work together to retrieve their family's lost wealth.

title: Maine Dil Tujhko Diya
subTitle: Ajay falls in love with Ayesha, a fellow college student who is the daughter of a rich businessman. However, problems arise when Ayesha's father arranges her marriage to an associate's son.

title: Dil Ka Rishta
subTitle: Jai, a wealthy businessman in love with Tia, accidentally kills her husband in a car crash. After the accident Tia loses her memory and falls for Jai, who struggles with guilt.
